Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buddhist tradition first came\Nto the land of snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,佛教传统\N是在公元前5世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the 5th century A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:00.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,首次出现在雪域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first Tibetan king to be touched\Nby the dharma
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第一位受达摩大师\N感化的藏王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was King Hathatha Rignamputsan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:04.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是哈塔塔·日男菩萨王.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他还有他的继位者\N都是众所周知的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and succeeding kings\Nwere collectively known
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the Happy Generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快乐传人.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, some historians place them\Nin a Water Snake year, 21 3 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:13.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 有的历史学家认为\N他是公元前水蛇年213年出生的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Others in the year of a Water Ox,\N1 73 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其他学者则认为他是公元前水牛年173年,\N出生的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, isn't it?\NThe Happy Generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很神奇吧?\N快乐传人.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper, l am thrilled to pieces\Nthat the dharma came
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员, 达摩大师转世\N成为那个什么鬼呵呵呵国王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to King Ho-Ho-Ho, l really am,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很振奋人心,真的,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but l'm trying to focus\Non the more immediate problems
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:26.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我更关心的是\N目前的这个案子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of our own century here\Nin Twin Peaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有我们自己的纪元\N和双峰镇.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, you'd be surprised\Nat the connection between the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾伯特, 你会惊奇的发现\N其实两者之间是有联系的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Color me amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,少来忽悠我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ronette Pulaski\Nhas woken from her coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:38.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,朗尼特·珀拉斯奇\N已经醒过来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:39.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm thinking she's gonna have\Nquite a story to tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:43.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定有很多话\N要和我们说,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- when she regains the ability to speak.\N- So she's not talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 等她恢复语言能力的时候.\N- 什么,她还不能说话?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waking but silent, probably shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:50.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,醒了但失语, 可能惊吓过度造成的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna show her the sketches\Nof Leo Johnson and Bob,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会给她看里欧·强生\N和鲍勃的人像素描,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the man Sarah Palmer saw\Nin her vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉·帕尔默看到了\N鲍勃的幻象.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who came to me\Nin my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也曾经出现过\N在我的梦里 .
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone seen Bob on Earth\Nin the last few weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,过去几周到底有没有人\N见过这个所谓的鲍勃?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:03.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有, 还没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. l performed the autopsy\Non Jacques Renault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:07.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧. 我对雅克·雷诺\N进行了解剖.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stomach contents revealed--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,胃部的残余物显示--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.\N--beer cans, a Maryland license plate,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:12.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看.\N--啤酒馆, 一块马里兰州的车牌,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,half a bicycle tire, a goat\Nand a small wooden puppet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:16.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,半条自行车胎, 一只山羊\N和一个小木偶,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,goes by the name of Pinocchio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,木偶皮诺曹.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在捉弄我.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l like to think of myself\Nas one of the Happy Generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我这么有幽默感\N就转世做快乐传人了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And by the way,\Nthe fat boy wasn't strangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊还有,\N那肥仔不是给勒死的.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killer snuffed him with a pillow.\NHe was wearing gloves,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是给枕头闷死的.\N凶手带着手套,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tape used to bind his wrists\Nwas stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,用来绑他手腕的带子\N是从医院的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the hospital supply closet.\NThat is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,储物室里偷来的.\N就这些了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf Jacques has any secrets\Nhe'll be taking them underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:35.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果雅克还有什么秘密\N也只带着下葬了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What about the mill?\N- Well, preliminary suggests arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 锯木厂呢?\N- 嗯, 初步确认是纵火案.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l nominate Leo Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:42.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我指证里欧·强生.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to get a statement\Nfrom Shelly Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们要给雪莉·强生\N发一份指证书.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hospital says she's well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,医院说她已经康复了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:49.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Me?\N- l believe it's customary to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我?\N- 只是循例问一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after the health of one\Nrecently plugged three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个给枪重创了\N3下的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢关心.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 少来耍感性啊.\N- 谁开的枪, 艾伯特?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't get sentimental.\N- Who shot me, Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My men are interrogating\Nthe hotel guests,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人正在审问\N酒店里的人,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the usual bumper crop\Nof rural know-nothings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,收获不大\N那些土佬什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and drunken fly fishermen.\NNothing so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个醉气熏天的卖鱼佬.\N目前为止还没进展.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's most decrepit\Nroom service waiter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个\N史上最老客服生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说那晚没发现\N任何异常.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,remembers nothing out of the ordinary\Nabout the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No surprise there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么突破.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senor Droolcup has, shall we say,\Na mind that wanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:19.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说,\N朱凯先生那晚是在神游.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, my ring is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:24.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾伯特, 我的戒指不见了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day here, the next day gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那天还在, 今天就没了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm glad you're with us, Albert.\NWe need the very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:36.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你在，艾伯特.\N我们这里需要人才.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dedication to duty wasn't the only thing\Nthat brought me back here, Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不光是回来这里\N义务劳动的, 库珀.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What else?\N- Windom Earle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是什么?\N- 伟顿·厄尔.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Earle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,厄尔探员?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是退休了吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a nice comfy chair\Ncomplete with wrist restraints
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就在当地的喜剧学院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the local laughing academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一张漂亮舒服有护腕的椅子上.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your former partner\Nflew the coop, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的前搭档\N秘密潜逃了, 库.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He escaped. Vanished into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他跑了. 消失得无影无踪.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Tremond? Meals on Wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:12.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,屈梦太太? 我来送餐的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,进来.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Tremond?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,屈梦太太?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l put your meal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,放这里好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 就放那吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 你好.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes things\Ncan happen just like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:58.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有时有些事可以\N这样玩法:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creamed corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:10.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,奶油玉米.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见了吗\N碟子里有奶油玉米?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see creamed corn\Non that plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看见.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l requested no creamed corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:25.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要奶油玉米.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see creamed corn\Non that plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:32.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见了吗\N碟子里有奶油玉米?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandson is studying magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:50.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我孙子在学魔术.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那不错.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm taking over Laura Palmer's place\Non the Meals on Wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是代替劳拉·帕尔默\N来送餐的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:18.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你对她了解吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know her well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mrs. Tremond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 屈梦太太.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll be back tomorrow to pick this up\Nand to bring your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:39.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天会过来给你送餐\N顺便把这些收拾了.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They used to bring me\Nhospital food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:43.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们以前给我送\N那些难吃的医院餐,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个珍妮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lmagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might ask Mr. Smith next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:55.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以问问住隔壁的史密斯先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was Laura's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他是劳拉的朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Smith does not leave his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:10.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯先生从不离开房子半步.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:58.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎是个不错的女生.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed like a very nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ronette?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,朗尼特?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't get this thing to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:23.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这椅子怎么搞的.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us, Ronette.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 朗尼特.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"等等.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read operating instructions\Nbeneath seat before using.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:42.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,使用前请阅读\N椅子下面的操作说明.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stand next to chair or stool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要站在凳子旁.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not remain seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要坐在椅子上.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,用脚踩着底座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Place foot on base
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把椅子完全拉起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pull seat all the way up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until you hear a click.''
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,直到听到「卡拉」 一声.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉, 朗尼特.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ronette.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ronette,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:23.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,朗尼特,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能听见我说话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm glad you're feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:31.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你好点了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want to upset you,\Nbut we need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:35.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想打搅你\N当我们需要你的帮助.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:39.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一些人像素描\N要给你辨认.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna show you some sketches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:43.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要知道\N你见过哪几个.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to know\Nif you've seen these men before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to know if these\Nare the men that hurt you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:47.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是他们\N袭击你的, 可以?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,认得这个男人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recognize this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this the man that hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是他袭击你的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,朗尼特.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ronette.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train. Train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,火车. 火车.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 朗尼特?\N- 火-- 车, 火车.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ronette?\N- Tr-- Train, train.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nurse. Right away.\N- Train?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 叫护士. 快.\N- 火车?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 火车?\N- 火--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Train?\N- Tra--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in the train car? Train car?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:01.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在火车里吗? 火车吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train, train, train!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,火车, 火车, 火车!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 是, 是! 火车!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, yeah! Train!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 好. 冷静.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:12.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,火车, 火车.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train, train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:17.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本哥,\N我们有两本帐本,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Ben,\Nwe've got two ledgers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one smoked cheese pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:21.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和一只烟熏芝士猪.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要烧哪一样?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one do we burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it ain't gonna be my pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不会是我的芝士猪吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real ledger shows the mill\Nslowly seeking into bankruptcy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:36.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个真帐本详细的记录了\N锯木厂破产的实际情况,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,masterminded by Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳一手策划的.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one she faked,\Nfor public consumption,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:42.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这本假的,\N是公开资料,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好让人觉得\N它仍在盈利.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shows the mill\Nturning a healthy profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So which one do we burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:50.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那到底烧哪一本?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳死了,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we put all of our money on Josie,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把钱全压在乔西身上了,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine takes the fall for the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:00.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑟琳做纵火案的替罪羊,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西得到保险赔偿,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie pockets the insurance money,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sells us the mill and the land and--\NNo, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:08.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把锯木厂连地皮一起卖给我们，然后--\N不是, 等等.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:13.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她必须先让亲爱的皮特\N签字才行.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First she has to get dear Pete\Nto sign on the dotted line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Pete have to sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:17.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要皮特签字?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:22.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安德鲁的遗嘱定下\N凯瑟琳或她的继承人同意签字才能卖.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andrew's will calls for Catherine\Nor her heirs to approve of any sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:26.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那到底要烧哪一本?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So which one do we burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦乔西把她卖给我们,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Josie sells us the mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果地价上涨\N我们就可以买个好价钱了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we could get a better price\Nif it appears to be more profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那把真的那本烧了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we burn the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但另一方面,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the real one would hold up\Nunder any future scrutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:43.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,万一以后有什么变化\N真的那本就能派上用场.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending upon how one looks\Nat the situation, it appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:50.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要视情况而定\N兵来将挡，水来土掩...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they both have merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...看来两本都有价值.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许两本都应该烧掉.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should burn both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt looks like we are 1 00 percent certain\Nthat we're not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:03.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一可以肯定地就是\N我们什么都不肯定.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:09.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰, 肯定要\N烧掉一些东西的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jer, obviously something\Nrequires burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:15.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要不就\N烧你的烟熏芝士猪,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since we don't wanna set fire\Nto your smoked cheese pig,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:20.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么不...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:23.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...尝尝这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...try these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,棉花糖!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marshmallows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本, 那些烧烤叉在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben, where are those hickory sticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:29.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,玛格利特,\N很高兴你常来.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margaret,\Nit's always very nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你要\N吐黏糊糊的口香糖时,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're gonna spit\Nyour sticky pitch gum out in the diner,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:35.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请吐到烟灰缸里,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please use an ashtray,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and not the counter or the booth\Nlike you did last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:38.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要像上次那样\N在柜台和卡座里乱吐，好么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一只熊掌.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll have a bear claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你胸口上戴的那些东西\N很闪亮.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wear shiny objects\Non your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你感到骄傲吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you proud?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:09.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 没什么好骄傲的.\N骄兵必败.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, achievement is its own reward.\NPride obscures it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加奶精吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的灵木有话要和你说.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My log has something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't believe\Nwe've been introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没介绍\N我们认识呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l do not introduce the log.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:30.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来不介绍我的灵木.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能听见它说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 夫人, 我听不见.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, ma'am, l cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我翻译.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:50.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去送消息.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliver the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:55.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 夫人. 我想我懂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am. As a matter of fact l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天没信, 布伦南副警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No messages, Deputy Brennan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说, 露西·默恩.\N只管听我说.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Lucy Moran.\NYou just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,科玛纽精子银行\N有一次在招捐精志愿者,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Tacoma Sperm Bank\Nwas looking for donors,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,naturally l applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:26.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这是市民的责任,\N而且我喜欢鲸鱼.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's my civic duty,\Nand l like whales.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:32.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是一个常规体检\N显示我有不育症.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A routine physical examination\Nrevealed that l'm sterile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然, 刚开始\N我想可能搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, l thought it meant\Nl didn't have to take a bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但后来医生亲口告诉我的.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the doctors told me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:41.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说我不会有小孩的.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me l can't have babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:48.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以, 我现在想知道\N你为什么会怀上，怎么怀上的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what l wanna know now is\Nwhy you're having one and how?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 汉克.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西一定和你说过\N要在外面等吧, 呵?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l bet Lucy asked you\Nto wait outside, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:44.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大概说过吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might've.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:50.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道,把雄鹿杀了\N作标本真太可怕了, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,\Nthat's an awfully cute buck, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:55.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别浪费时间了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not waste our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:56.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:21:59.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...不能乖乖的签了它呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just sign in like a good boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,规规矩矩的\N过好下一周.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your nose clean\Nfor another week.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:29.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,又见到你了，真好.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's really nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:46.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lnteresting piece of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你和汉克\N认识多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long were you\Nand Hank friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We grew up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:52.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从小一起长大.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,汉克以前也是\N书屋会的成员.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hank used to be\Na Bookhouse Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:22:58.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当时...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.06,0:23:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hank was one of the best of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:01.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...汉克是我们中间最棒的一个.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff Truman, I have Ben Horne\Non the phone for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:05.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}杜鲁门警长, 本·荷恩\N找你.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:07.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮你\N转进来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me\Nto transfer him to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:10.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 不是转他是转电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not him but his phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:14.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,接进来, 露西.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put him on, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:20.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩,先生 我是露西.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Horne, this is Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:24.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}现在帮你转接到\N杜鲁门警长的办公室.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna transfer you now\Ninto Sheriff Truman's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:27.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}他现在和\N特派探员戴尔·库珀一起.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in there with\NSpeciaI Agent DaIe Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 请稍等.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:39.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杜鲁门警长,\N本·荷恩转进来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff Truman,\Nl've transferred Ben Horne to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:43.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正在闪灯的\N那条线.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Iine with the Iight\Nthat's bIinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:47.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是, 本.\N- 哈里...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, Ben.\N- Harry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:49.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...欧蕊失踪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Audrey's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:53.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么?\N- 已经两天没见人了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- For as much as maybe two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:23:55.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你等等.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.11,0:23:58.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊·荷恩失踪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:23:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey Horne is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:16.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一张, 还没签成的保险单.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One insurance policy, unsigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.36,0:24:17.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"没签成"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Un''?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:21.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个保险经纪说\N凯瑟琳觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.04,0:24:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The agent said that Catherine\Nwas concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.92,0:24:24.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,保单有些地方不对劲.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about certain irregularities.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.22,0:24:28.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,比如保单的最大受益人\N被改成了乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.24,0:24:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such as Josie being named\Nthe chief beneficiary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.00,0:24:31.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个保险经纪\N不应该告诉她的.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.05,0:24:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent wasn't supposed\Nto show it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.26,0:24:35.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦, 既然凯瑟琳\N都已经死于非命了,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.28,0:24:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, considering\NCatherine's smoky fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.60,0:24:38.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就当给她打堂斋吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.62,0:24:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for our side, it's all for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.86,0:24:44.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,算了. 有得必有失.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.89,0:24:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well. Win a few, lose a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.73,0:24:49.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快点打电话给那些\N烂醉如泥的冰岛佬吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.76,0:24:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get those pickled icemen\Non the blower.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.67,0:24:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen,\Nl've been giving this a lot of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.68,0:24:56.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,先生们,\N我已经仔细研究过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.59,0:24:59.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为锯木厂的火灾\N合约的签署可能要推迟,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.61,0:24:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mill fire will put contract signing\Non hold for the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.67,0:25:02.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得马上行动,\N马上, 别让机会溜走.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.68,0:25:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we must ensure that the moment,\Nour moment, does not pass us by.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.18,0:25:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l therefore recommend\Nwe make a quick
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.19,0:25:04.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我建议\N立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.97,0:25:06.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,致电冰岛\N诚恳地通知他们,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.98,0:25:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but cordial follow-up phone call\Nto lceland,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.93,0:25:07.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安抚一下他们,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.95,0:25:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a little gentle handling,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.14,0:25:10.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也好让艾尼了解\N我们会把事情及时处理好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.15,0:25:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let Einer know\Nthat we're right on top of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.84,0:25:13.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会摆平的.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.86,0:25:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.57,0:25:15.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请找艾尼·霍尔森，我是本·荷恩.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.59,0:25:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ben Horne for Einer Thorson.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.92,0:25:19.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看,我们心有灵犀 .
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.96,0:25:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this is a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.57,0:25:23.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾尼.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.60,0:25:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Einer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.87,0:25:28.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.87,0:25:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.91,0:25:32.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么知道火灾的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.94,0:25:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.56,0:25:37.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是帕尔默先生\N打电话告诉你的?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.61,0:25:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Palmer called\Nto tell you about the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.38,0:25:43.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 不, 绝对不是\N什么天灾人祸.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.39,0:25:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, l wouldn't call it\Na disaster at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.07,0:25:47.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是发展过程里的,\N一个小小意外.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.12,0:25:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's just one of those things,\Nan unfortunate development.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:49.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可以向你保证, 艾尼,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.96,0:25:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l assure you, Einer,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.28,0:25:52.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么\N都不会影响我们的发展大计.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.33,0:25:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it in no way\Nwill affect our development plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.93,0:25:54.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾尼，我是杰利·荷恩.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.97,0:25:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry Horne here, Einer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.19,0:25:57.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑，我们将全力以赴.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.20,0:25:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.62,0:26:01.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 是的, 当然, 艾尼.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.67,0:26:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, of course, Einer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.62,0:26:04.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会尽快把详细报告\N传真给你.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.64,0:26:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will fax all pertinent details\Nto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.97,0:26:06.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 是的, 我保证.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.01,0:26:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, l promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.27,0:26:10.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说, 希望你别为这事\N心烦意乱.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.31,0:26:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, l don't want you to worry\Nyour attractive blond head about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.88,0:26:13.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾尼, 我还要开会, 先这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.88,0:26:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Einer, l'm in a meeting, gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.39,0:26:17.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.42,0:26:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.83,0:26:21.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰, 我看这样吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.86,0:26:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland, here's an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.74,0:26:23.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,合约的事\N你就先别管了,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.76,0:26:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take you off of\Ndamage control,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.17,0:26:27.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不如你先帮我\N处理一下其他事务吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.20,0:26:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let you concentrate on something\Nthat you can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.39,0:26:29.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,填填那些纳税申报单之类的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.40,0:26:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like my tax return.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.29,0:26:37.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识他.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.34,0:26:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:39.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.18,0:26:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.24,0:26:47.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我祖父在珍珠湖\N有座避暑山庄.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.25,0:26:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandfather's summer house\Non Pearl Lakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.67,0:26:50.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他就住在隔壁.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.72,0:26:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lived right next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.15,0:26:54.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我那时还很小.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.19,0:26:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was just a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.45,0:26:58.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我认得他.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.46,0:26:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.53,0:27:04.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我得马上去\N通报警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.57,0:27:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've gotta tell the sheriff\Nabout this right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.10,0:27:08.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杰利...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.11,0:27:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.61,0:27:11.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...拜托你杀了利兰吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.68,0:27:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please kill Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.13,0:27:17.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗, 本,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.18,0:27:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this real, Ben,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.52,0:27:22.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是个变态的梦吧?\N还是我们都疯了?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.55,0:27:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or some strange and\Ntwisted dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.08,0:27:28.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那颗子弹嵌在里欧的脊椎骨里--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.12,0:27:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bullet lodged in Leo's spine--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.86,0:27:31.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心, 雪莉, 会好起来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.89,0:27:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all right, Shelly, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.33,0:27:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bullet lodged in his spine,\Nbut we removed it successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.34,0:27:36.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,子弹是嵌在他的脊椎骨里,\N但我们已经成功把它取出来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.20,0:27:40.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,至于会不会瘫痪,\N现在还很难说.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.23,0:27:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for possible paralysis,\Nit's too early to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.37,0:27:41.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想动一次手术,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.41,0:27:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo lost a lot of blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.02,0:27:44.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但里欧已经\N失血过多.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.07,0:27:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,most of it before we had a chance\Nto operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.94,0:27:48.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,导致脑部严重缺氧\N这种昏迷状态下再动手术,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.98,0:27:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l fear the resulting oxygen deprivation\Nstarved his brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.45,0:27:51.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕他的身体承受不了.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.48,0:27:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,induced the coma you see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.41,0:27:54.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他成了植物人?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.45,0:27:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls he a vegetable?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.53,0:27:58.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那他会痛苦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.59,0:27:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls he in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.97,0:28:00.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他感觉不到痛苦.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.99,0:28:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.92,0:28:03.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很难解释, 不是你想像的那样.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.96,0:28:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that, it's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.44,0:28:07.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你能治好他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.46,0:28:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make him better?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.83,0:28:10.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,目前我们只能维持他的现状.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.87,0:28:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can maintain his current state.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.26,0:28:14.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,打流质营业, 用维生仪器.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.30,0:28:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Offer nutrition, life-support.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.43,0:28:18.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外\N我们只能等待.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.47,0:28:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that the only ally\Nwe have is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.04,0:28:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.04,0:28:21.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很难过, 雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.91,0:28:23.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.95,0:28:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.42,0:28:26.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他会坐牢吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.45,0:28:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gonna put him in prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.99,0:28:31.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他现在\N是几个重案的嫌疑人.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know he's a suspect\Nin several felonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.59,0:28:37.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来这牢\N他是坐定了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.63,0:28:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess at the moment\Nhe's kind of in prison anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.59,0:28:39.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.63,0:28:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.10,0:28:55.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧, 我还是先\N送你回房收拾吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.14,0:28:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, l'll take you back\Nto your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.31,0:29:00.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,诺玛来接你回家了\N她在楼下等着呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.35,0:29:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Norma's waiting downstairs\Nto drive you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.17,0:29:16.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好, 双峰镇警察局.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.20,0:29:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Twin Peaks Sheriff's Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.38,0:29:19.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请问哪里找?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.40,0:29:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who may l say is calling, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.51,0:29:23.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 你要告诉我\N你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.54,0:29:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, l can't connect you\Nwith Sheriff Truman
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.47,0:29:26.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,否则，电话不能\N转给杜鲁门警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.51,0:29:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you tell me\Nwhat your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.25,0:29:29.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能说?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.31,0:29:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.16,0:29:33.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉, 那我不能转给\N杜鲁门警长
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.18,0:29:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, but l can't connect you\Nwith Sheriff Truman
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.41,0:29:36.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除非告诉我你名字.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.45,0:29:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.85,0:29:43.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,实在很抱歉 ,\N你再不说我就要挂机了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.89,0:29:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm terribly sorry,\Nbut l'm going to have to hang up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.04,0:30:05.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 我来送吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.08,0:30:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, l'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.87,0:30:07.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不. 不, 你不行.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.92,0:30:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.78,0:30:09.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没事, 怕什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.85,0:30:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.69,0:30:13.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧, 小心别打烂了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.72,0:30:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but watch out for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.60,0:30:15.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.63,0:30:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.65,0:31:04.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛把吸尘器关了?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.67,0:31:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the vacuum cleaner off?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.73,0:31:06.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这些脚指头.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.78,0:31:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.08,0:31:08.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,脚指头怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.11,0:31:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What toes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.77,0:31:11.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我送冰来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.81,0:31:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l brought the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.56,0:31:15.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,送来啦? 我的小雪人.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.62,0:31:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frosty? My little snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.42,0:31:19.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得凉飕飕的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.45,0:31:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel a cold front moving in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.46,0:31:24.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨呀, 艾默里.\N还记得我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.49,0:31:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Emory.\NYou remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.24,0:31:28.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来\N你很会享受嘛, 哼?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.30,0:31:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt really looks like you got yourself\Nin a fix here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.80,0:31:29.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 猜猜看.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.83,0:31:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess what.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.11,0:31:32.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我要给你讲一个\N很好听的童话故事. 准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.14,0:31:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going to tell you a nice\Nlittle bedtime story. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.28,0:31:37.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前\N一个很傻很天真地女孩, 叫小红帽--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.34,0:31:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time there was\Na sweet, innocent girl named Red--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.41,0:31:38.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.48,0:31:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.62,0:31:41.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,--然后她碰到了大坏狼--\N也就是你.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.68,0:31:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and she met a bad old wolf--\NThat's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.75,0:31:45.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,--她狠狠的揍了大坏狼一顿之后\N还告诉了她爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.81,0:31:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and she kicked the crap out of that\Nwolf and she told her daddy all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.18,0:31:47.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和警察叔叔,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.22,0:31:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she told the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.40,0:31:50.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,结果又老又丑的大坏狼\N被判刑坐一百万年牢.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.45,0:31:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the bad old wolf\Nwent to jail for a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.44,0:31:53.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你到底想怎样?\N- 把你知道事的都告诉我.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.49,0:31:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you want?\N- l want to know everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.39,0:31:57.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,香水专柜, 劳拉·帕尔默,\N朗尼特·珀拉斯奇和单眼杰克赌场.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.46,0:31:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfume counter, Laura Palmer,\NRonette Pulaski and One-Eyed Jack's.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.91,0:31:59.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.96,0:31:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.21,0:32:01.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我疯了?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.23,0:32:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.56,0:32:04.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,听着, 我是欧蕊·荷恩\N我爱干嘛就干嘛.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.60,0:32:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l'm Audrey Horne\Nand l get what l want.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.56,0:32:06.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 懂了没?\N- 是, 听到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.60,0:32:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Understand?\N- Yes, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.99,0:32:09.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我替单眼杰克赌场\N的老板干活.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.04,0:32:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l work for the owner\Nof One-Eyed Jack's.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.03,0:32:12.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谁是老板?\N- 我替单眼杰克赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.08,0:32:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who is?\N- l work for the owner
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.20,0:32:14.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 的老板干活.\N- 他是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.24,0:32:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- of One-Eyed Jack's.\N- Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.81,0:32:15.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.85,0:32:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.29,0:32:18.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,赌场是他的.\N真见鬼, 所有东西都是他的.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.35,0:32:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He owns it all.\NHell, he owns everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.11,0:32:20.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我负责把香水专柜\N的女生介绍进来.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.12,0:32:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l run girls through\Nthe perfume counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.20,0:32:23.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也包括朗尼特和劳拉.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.22,0:32:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l recruited Ronette and Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.15,0:32:26.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 劳拉在这呆过?\N- 有一个周末.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.19,0:32:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did Laura come here?\N- One weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.41,0:32:28.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她嗑了药.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.42,0:32:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was using drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.76,0:32:31.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就把她扔了出去.\N之后再没见过她了, 我发誓.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.79,0:32:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We threw her out.\Nl never saw her again, l swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.23,0:32:33.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸知道\N劳拉在这呆过吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.26,0:32:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did my father know\Nthat Laura was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.19,0:32:34.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 是的, 他当然知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.23,0:32:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.62,0:32:39.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩先生经常\N来和她们玩.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.63,0:32:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Horne makes it his business\Nto entertain all the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.79,0:32:42.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道是我爸的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.81,0:32:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she know he owned this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.70,0:32:43.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.74,0:32:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owned what?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.96,0:32:47.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 赌场!\N- 是! 是. 有可能知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.01,0:32:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- One-Eyed Jack's!\N- Yes! Yes. Probably she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.13,0:32:49.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉总有法子的.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.15,0:32:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura always got her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.04,0:32:53.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.08,0:32:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.48,0:32:55.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.52,0:32:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.12,0:33:12.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛不换个台.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.14,0:33:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you change the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.68,0:33:16.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个好.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.74,0:33:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.67,0:33:20.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唔.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.74,0:33:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.11,0:33:24.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我打过电话给保险公司了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.15,0:33:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l made the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.10,0:33:27.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我说是里欧的堂兄.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.15,0:33:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Told them l was Leo's cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.71,0:33:28.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧现在残废了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.75,0:33:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo gets his disability
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.10,0:33:32.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他监狱外服刑.\N就可以得到一大笔赔偿金, 知道吗，雪莉.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.15,0:33:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as he stays out of prison.\Nlt's a lot of money, Shelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.79,0:33:34.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,五千多一个月.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.82,0:33:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 5,000 a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.79,0:33:38.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但条件是\N他必须呆在家里.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.83,0:33:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you only get it\Nif he stays at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.40,0:33:42.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要什么赔偿金.\N我不想里欧回家.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.46,0:33:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't care about the money.\Nl don't want Leo home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.74,0:33:46.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经半个死人了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.80,0:33:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo is in dreamland.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.18,0:33:50.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,随你摆布，塞他到墙角也行\N在他耳朵上挂面包甜甜圈都行.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.20,0:33:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stick him in the corner\Nand hang doughnuts from his ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.78,0:33:52.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可是杜鲁门警长\N想我出庭作证人.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.81,0:33:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff Truman wants me\Nto make a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.82,0:33:56.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了. 瞧, 他们怎么能强迫你\N去指证自己的丈夫呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.84,0:33:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Look, they can't force you\Nto testify against your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.78,0:33:59.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做的\N是把里欧接回家,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.82,0:33:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you gotta do is get Leo home,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.29,0:34:02.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,等着收支票享福去.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.35,0:34:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sit and collect the checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.16,0:34:07.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是里欧欠你的, 宝贝儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.19,0:34:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo owes you, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.81,0:34:09.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,该他还债了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.86,0:34:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can really make him pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.03,0:34:11.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有了这些钱\N我们什么都买的起.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.10,0:34:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want something nice?\NWe can buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.72,0:34:15.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以周游列国,\N去日光浴?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.80,0:34:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go someplace special,\Nsit in the sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.59,0:34:17.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就靠里欧了. 明白没?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.63,0:34:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's on Leo. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.58,0:34:26.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也好吧\N不用老为钱发愁.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.64,0:34:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess it would be nice\Nnot to have to worry about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.93,0:34:29.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有很多帐单没还呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.98,0:34:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have a lot of bills l have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.62,0:34:34.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,帐单? 想那个干嘛.\N我现在讨论的是一个美好的未来.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.68,0:34:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bills? Forget about bills.\Nl'm talking about a new way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.83,0:34:40.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,共同奋斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.86,0:34:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.08,0:34:49.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.13,0:34:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.16,0:34:59.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在只想爽爽.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.21,0:34:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think l wanna get comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.25,0:35:03.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那得尝尝我爸传给我的那杆大烟枪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.28,0:35:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why l got my dad's Continental.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.59,0:35:13.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比·布里格斯,\N看我不把你生吞了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.65,0:35:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby Briggs,\Nl'm gonna eat you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.37,0:35:16.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来吞啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.43,0:35:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.62,0:35:19.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我走着瞧.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.70,0:35:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.49,0:35:30.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黛安, 今天接到\N好几个坏消息.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.54,0:35:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, l received\Nsome very bad news today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.44,0:35:33.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伟顿·厄尔失踪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.48,0:35:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windom Earle has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.44,0:35:36.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的前搭档\N莫名其妙的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.48,0:35:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The disappearance\Nof my former partner
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.74,0:35:39.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,着实让人感到不安.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.78,0:35:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is extremely troubling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.69,0:35:43.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊·荷恩\N也失踪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.75,0:35:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l also learned that Audrey Horne\Nis missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.65,0:35:49.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没料到\N欧蕊会失踪.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.72,0:35:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey's absence touches me\Nin ways l could not predict.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.82,0:35:53.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除了她的\N那张笑脸,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.89,0:35:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l find myself thinking not of clues\Nor of evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.42,0:35:56.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其他线索我毫无头绪.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.47,0:35:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but of the content of her smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.16,0:36:01.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.24,0:36:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.16,0:36:05.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员，是我，布里格斯少校.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.21,0:36:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Major Briggs, Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.80,0:36:15.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马上来.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.85,0:36:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.97,0:36:23.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 少校.\N- 我可以进来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.99,0:36:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Major.\N- May l come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.23,0:36:24.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请进.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.29,0:36:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.39,0:36:34.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给你带个口信.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.44,0:36:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.13,0:36:36.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谁的口信?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.17,0:36:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.26,0:36:41.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,基于我工作的特殊性\N恕我不能直说.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.31,0:36:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not at liberty\Nto reveal the nature of my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.73,0:36:44.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知者不能言\N有时确实让我很痛苦.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.78,0:36:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This secrecy pains me\Nfrom time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.86,0:36:47.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,任何官僚制度下\N都有一套保护自身秘密的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.88,0:36:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any bureaucracy\Nthat functions in secret
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.90,0:36:51.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可它又反过来增加了更多不可告人的腐败秘密.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.95,0:36:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inevitably lends itself to corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.90,0:36:54.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我发过誓\N必须要捍卫它.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.96,0:36:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these rules l have pledged\Nto uphold.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.90,0:36:56.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我始终相信有些信念神圣不可侵犯.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.96,0:36:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l believe a pledge is sacred.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.33,0:36:58.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,作为联邦政府的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.36,0:36:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking as a man
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.55,0:37:01.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,公务员和代言人\N我理解你.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.56,0:37:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a fellow employee\Nof the federal government, so do l.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.46,0:37:04.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 我或许只能透露这些给你:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.50,0:37:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l may reveal this much:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.32,0:37:06.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在我执行的众多任务中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.37,0:37:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among my many tasks
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.37,0:37:09.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一项就是对\N瞄准外层太空银河系
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.40,0:37:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the maintenance\Nof deep-space monitors
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.67,0:37:12.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的监测器进行维修和保养.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.71,0:37:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aimed at galaxies beyond our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.40,0:37:17.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的日常事务\N就是接收些五花八门的信号,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.48,0:37:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We routinely receive\Nvarious communications,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.10,0:37:21.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也有些太空垃圾,\N然后进行解码和检测.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.15,0:37:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,space garbage,\Nto decode and examine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.62,0:37:23.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，它们是这样子的.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.69,0:37:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.96,0:37:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's radio waves and gibberish,\NAgent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.13,0:37:30.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,无线电波和一些乱七八糟的信息代码,\N库珀探员.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.04,0:37:34.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道周四晚.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.10,0:37:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Till Thursday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.69,0:37:36.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是周五的凌晨.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.73,0:37:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friday morning to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.17,0:37:39.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我中枪的那晚.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.24,0:37:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time that l was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.95,0:37:45.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当晚的资料分析把我们吓了一跳.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.01,0:37:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The readout took us by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.60,0:37:48.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一排接一排讥哩咕噜的鬼话之后.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.68,0:37:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Row after row of gibberish.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.29,0:37:50.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现了这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.35,0:37:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.16,0:37:54.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"不要给猫头鹰的外表迷惑了."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.22,0:37:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''The owls are not what they seem.''
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.54,0:38:04.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么告诉我这些?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.60,0:38:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.67,0:38:09.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那天凌晨之后...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.73,0:38:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because later in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.66,0:38:11.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"库珀...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.74,0:38:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Cooper...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.62,0:38:18.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...库珀. 库珀."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.64,0:38:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Cooper. Cooper.''
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.27,0:38:21.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.35,0:38:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.26,0:38:30.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚唱的不错.\N我们再来一次吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.35,0:38:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was really good.\NLet's try it again.
