Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.81,0:41:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.11,0:41:43.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.18,0:41:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.50,0:41:45.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.58,0:41:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.89,0:41:47.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.95,0:41:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.58,0:41:52.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.66,0:41:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.58,0:41:53.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 到底怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.62,0:41:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.75,0:41:55.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有点激动, 詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.83,0:41:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm trembling, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.10,0:41:58.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你让我好激动.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.16,0:41:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.44,0:42:01.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.50,0:42:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.57,0:42:06.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.64,0:42:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.44,0:42:08.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.51,0:42:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.83,0:42:13.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你的电话\N是哈罗德·史密斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.87,0:42:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a telephone call for you\Nfrom a Harold Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.43,0:42:17.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 好的. 我在走廊听.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.48,0:42:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. l'll get it in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.55,0:42:30.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 爸. 我在听呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.63,0:42:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Dad. l got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.77,0:42:32.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的, 宝贝儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.83,0:42:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.07,0:42:36.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.13,0:42:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.19,0:42:39.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.24,0:42:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.89,0:42:45.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.97,0:42:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l received yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.06,0:42:49.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你当面谈谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.15,0:42:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.75,0:42:53.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能见面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.82,0:42:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.62,0:42:56.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.69,0:42:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.38,0:44:25.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要给猫头鹰的外表迷惑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.44,0:44:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owls are not what they seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.06,0:44:35.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要给猫头鹰的外表迷惑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.12,0:44:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owls are not what they seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.97,0:44:49.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}劳拉!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.03,0:44:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.27,0:44:53.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}劳拉!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.34,0:44:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.55,0:45:14.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀探员.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.62,0:45:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.86,0:45:17.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是我, 欧蕊.\N- 鸥蕊?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.96,0:45:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- lt's me, Audrey.\N- Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.85,0:45:19.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.90,0:45:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.25,0:45:20.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么没有来?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.33,0:45:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.89,0:45:23.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 现在没时间\N玩过家家.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.97,0:45:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, this is no time\Nfor schoolgirl games.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.81,0:45:25.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你马上回家.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.87,0:45:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.37,0:45:29.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你穿礼服的样子.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.41,0:45:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l saw you in your tuxedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.28,0:45:31.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太帅了，就像电影明星.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.34,0:45:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a movie star.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.76,0:45:34.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}欧蕊,\N如果你是碰到什么麻烦的话--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.84,0:45:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey,\Nif you're in any kind of troubIe--
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.67,0:45:38.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是遇到麻烦了\N但我会马上回家的.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.78,0:45:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am in trouble\Nbut l'm gonna come home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.84,0:45:42.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊? 欧蕊?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.88,0:45:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey? Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.14,0:45:45.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦大了, 荷恩小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.22,0:45:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble, Miss Horne?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.40,0:45:48.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道有多大吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.49,0:45:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what trouble is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.35,0:45:52.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,总之会很大很大....
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.43,0:45:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not by a long shot.
